I"<h3 id="all-your-sketch-files-in-one-place">All your Sketch files in one place</h3>

<p>No more hunting through shared folders. Abstract is a safe home for your Sketch design and library files, a single source of truth for your design team’s work.</p>

<h3 id="version-control-for-sketch-files">Version control for Sketch files</h3>

<p>Stop relying on creative file-naming conventions. Abstract removes the friction of managing your team’s growing Sketch design files. It’s not just version control; it’s source control you can trust.</p>

<h3 id="no-more-conflicted-copies">No more conflicted copies</h3>

<p>Work on the same set of Sketch files without losing anyone’s work. Abstract allows multiple designers to work on the same file without fearing overwritten changes.booklink</p>
